I received the @JanssenUS J&J #COVID19 #vaccine, with deep gratitude for the scientists who enabled this, with solemn recollection of those who did not live to see this day.

Baruch atah, Adonai Eloheinu, Melech haolam, shehecheyanu, v'kiy'manu, v'higiyanu laz'man hazeh. https://t.co/ill9SIoyzp
